%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Be%20%26quot%3BStrong%20Opposition%26quot%3B%3A%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Party%20After%20Big%20Poll%20Losses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEx-Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnaveen-patnaik%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENaveen%20Patnaik%3C%2Fa%3E's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbjd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiju%20Janata%20Dal%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20which%20helped%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbjp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20pass%20key%20bills%20in%20the%20Modi%20government's%20first%20two%20terms%2C%20when%20it%20lacked%20numbers%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20-%20seems%20now%20to%20have%20switched%20sides%2C%20and%20has%20labelled%20itself%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20and%20vibrant%20opposition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20make%20the%20centre%20accountable%20on%20all%20issues.%20BJD%20MPs%20will%20raise%20all%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20state's%20development%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha.%20Many%20rightful%20demands%20haven't%20been%20met%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20quoted%20Mr%20Patnaik%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20nine%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(We%20will)%20be%20the%20voice%20of%204.5%20crore%20people%20of%20Odisha%20in%20Parliament...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20BJD%20backed%20the%20BJP%20on%20various%20issues%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20support%20from%20the%20BJD%20and%20ex-Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20-%20his%20YSR%20Congress%20was%20ousted%20by%20the%20BJP's%20ally%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20-%20was%20crucial%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20election%20of%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202009%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20BJD's%20support%20also%20helped%20the%20BJP%20push%20through%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%2C%20ensured%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20flopped%2C%20and%20pushed%20through%20laws%20like%20Triple%20Talaq%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Brightful%20demands%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJD's%20statement%20said%2C%20ranged%20from%20'special%20category'%20status%20for%20Odisha%20to%20housing%20and%20education%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20from%20establishment%20of%20premier%20medical%20institutions%20like%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20-%20%26quot%3B...%20not%20satellite%20units%26quot%3B%20-%20to%20improved%20national%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20flagged%20social%20and%20economic%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20controversial%20topic%20of%20MSP%2C%20or%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20for%20farmers%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20BJP%20since%20the%20violent%20protests%20of%202021%2F22.%20The%20BJD%20also%20said%20it%20will%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20inclusion%20of%20162%20communities%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state's%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%2C%20which%20it%20said%20it%20had%20been%20lobbying%20for%20%26quot%3Bfor%20many%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20comes%20after%20thumping%20wins%20by%20Mr%20Modi's%20party%20in%20the%20May-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections.%20In%20the%20former%20the%20BJP%20routed%20the%20BJD%20by%20winning%2020%20of%20the%20state's%2021%20seats%20and%2C%20in%20the%20latter%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20-%20who%20lost%20the%20Kantabanji%20seat%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Laxman%20Bag%20-%20won%20only%2051%20of%20147%2C%20down%20from%20112%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20BJP%20secured%2078%20-%20four%20over%20majority%20-%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-mohan-majhi-odishas-chief-minister-designate-5-points-5867952%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eform%20its%20first%20Odisha%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnaveen-patnaik-to-bjp-mla-in-odisha-assembly-oh-you-defeated-me-5917676%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20You%20Defeated%20Me%26quot%3B%3A%20BJD%20Boss%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20To%20BJP%20MLA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20twin%20defeats%20left%20Mr%20Patnaik%20firmly%20on%20the%20backfoot%20in%20a%20state%20he%20has%20dominated%20since%202000%3B%20his%20BJD%20had%20won%20every%20Assembly%20poll%20and%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20each%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20BJD%20has%20failed%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20to%20win%20even%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%2C%20which%20had%2012%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20in%202019%2C%20now%20has%20only%20nine%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20And%20that%20number%20will%20be%20cut%20in%20half%20in%202026%2C%20when%20four%20Odisha%20seats%20-%20now%20held%20by%20the%20BJD%20-%20fall%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20BJD%20leader%20Sasmit%20Patra%20said%20party%20boss%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20had%20given%20%26quot%3Bclear%20instructions%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20state's%20people%20in%20Parliament%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20support%20to%20BJP%2C%20only%20opposition.%20We%20may%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20Odisha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-more-support-to-bjp-only-opposition-naveen-patnaiks-party-mp-5958234%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20More%20Support%20To%20BJP%2C%20Only%20Opposition%26