ews%2Frevisiting-kargil-at-25-air-power-that-turned-the-tide-at-18-000-feet-5958961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20enemy%20had%20fortified%20its%20position%20at%2018%2C000%20feet%20on%20the%20icy%20heights%20of%20Kargil.%20A%20mass%20mobilization%20of%20troops%20began%20to%20evict%20the%20soldiers%20of%20Pakistan's%20Northern%20Light%20Infantry%20(NLI)%20disguised%20as%20militants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevisiting-kargil-at-25-air-power-that-turned-the-tide-at-18-000-feet-5958961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevisiting-kargil-at-25-air-power-that-turned-the-tide-at-18-000-feet-5958961%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevisiting-kargil-at-25-air-power-that-turned-the-tide-at-18-000-feet-5958961%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Months%20On%2C%20BJP%20Leader's%20Death%20Remains%20A%20Mystery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENine%20months%20after%20the%20unexplained%20death%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20leader%20Mamta%20Yadav%2C%20investigations%20involving%20the%20police%20of%20two%20states%20have%20produced%20no%20leads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20Mamta%20Yadav%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20her%20family%20in%20Ashoknagar%2C%20some%20200%20km%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20capital%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20is%20mired%20in%20bureaucratic%20inertia%20between%20the%20police%20departments%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Yadav's%20body%2C%20identified%20by%20a%20tattoo%2C%20was%20found%20in%20UP's%20Prayagraj.%20The%20family%20says%20they%20want%20to%20cremate%20her%20per%20Hindu%20rituals%20but%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20perform%20her%20last%20rites%20with%20dignity.%20The%20police%20must%20give%20us%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raina%20Bai%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamta%20Yadav%20went%20missing%20on%20September%2011%2C%202023.%20She%20told%20her%20family%20that%20she%20was%20traveling%20to%20Prayagraj%20to%20recover%20Rs%207%20lakh%20from%20an%20acquaintance.%20She%20last%20spoke%20to%20her%20brother%20on%20September%2021.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20vanished.%20Despite%20repeated%20requests%20from%20the%20family%2C%20the%20police%20allegedly%20delayed%20filing%20a%20missing%20person's%20report%2C%20and%20their%20searches%20yielded%20no%20results%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Rajbhan%2C%20Mamta's%20brother%2C%20was%20called%20by%20cops%20to%20Prayagraj%20to%20identify%20his%20sister%20from%20photographs%20of%20unclaimed%20bodies.%20The%20body%20was%20found%20on%20September%2026%2C%202023%2C%20and%20was%20buried%20by%20the%20police%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMamta%20had%20said%20her%20life%20was%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajbhan%2C%20recalling%20their%20telephonic%20conversation.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20our%20repeated%20appeals%2C%20the%20police%20offered%20little%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamta's%20brother%20disclosed%20that%20her%20sister%20had%20pen%20drives%20containing%20sensitive%20information%20about%20several%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20immense%20political%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed.%20%26quot%3BShe%20kept%20two%20pen%20drives%20in%20a%20locker%2C%20but%20never%20disclosed%20its%20contents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20been%20hamstrung%20by%20jurisdictional%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20body%20was%20recovered%20by%20Prayagraj%20police%2C%20making%20it%20their%20responsibility%20to%20investigate.%20We%20have%20handed%20over%20all%20evidence%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vineet%20Jain%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Ashoknagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20has%20called%20for%20a%20high-level%20investigation%20into%20the%20death%20of%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20written%20to%20the%20DGP%20(Director%20General%20of%20Police)%20demanding%20the%20NIA%20(National%20Investigation%20Agency)%20or%20STF%20(Special%20Task%20Force)%20take%20over%20this%20case.%20It's%20not%20a%20trivial%20matter%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20a%20BJP%20Mandal%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%2C%20expressing%20skepticism%20about%20a%20CBI%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20dismissed%20conspiracy%20theories%20surrounding%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719237240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvv99p8po_mamta-yadav-1200_625x300_24_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F9-months-on-bjp-leader-mamta-yadavs-death-remains-a-mystery-5960255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nine%20months%20after%20the%20unexplained%20death%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20leader%20Mamta%20Yadav%2C%20investigations%20involving%20the%20police%20of%20two%20states%20have%20produced%20no%20leads.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F9-months-on-bjp-leader-mamta-yadavs-death-remains-a-mystery-5960255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F9-months-on-bjp-leader-mamta-yadavs-death-remains-a-mystery-5960255%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F9-months-on-bjp-leader-mamta-yadavs-death-remains-a-mystery-5960255%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAre%20You%20Defending%20Lt%20Governor%3F%26quot%3B%20Court's%20Tough%20Talk%20On%20Delhi%20Tree%20Cutting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20in%20the%20capital's%20Ridge%20area%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20it%20cannot%20brush%20aside%20%26quot%3Bbrazen%20acts%26quot%3B%20that%20lead%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20authorities%20are%20not%20performing%20their%20statutory%20and%20constitutional%20duties%2C%20the%20court%20has%20to%20give%20a%20loud%20signal%20to%20all%20authorities%20that%20the%20environment%20cannot%20be%20damaged%20in%20such%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20which%20was%20hearing%20a%20suo%20motu%20contempt%20case%20against%20the%20DDA%20vice-president%2C%20also%20proposed%20a%20large-scale%20tree%20plantation%20drive%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20This%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20city%20reeled%20under%20an%20unrelenting%20heatwave%20that%20claimed%20many%20lives.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20DDA%20how%20a%20Tree%20Protection%20Act%20can%20be%20implemented%20and%20said%20it%20will%20give%20instructions%20to%20civic%20authorities%20to%20conduct%20a%20tree%20plantation%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vacation%20bench%20today%20fielded%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20DDA%20on%20how%20trees%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Ridge%20area%20were%20felled%20despite%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20against%20cutting%20trees%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20shocking%20if%20the%20trees%20were%20cut%20despite%20knowing%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20done%20without%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20said.%20He%20then%20asked%20if%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20had%20asked%20DDA%20officials%20to%20remove%20the%20trees.%20Mr%20Saxena%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20DDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20dealing%20with%20a%20very%20serious%20issue%3F%201100%20trees%2C%20you%20taking%20it%20very%20casually%3F%20Ask%20your%20officer%20who%20issued%20these%20directions...%20is%20it%20the%20chairman%3F%20Then%20we%20are%20making%20him%20a%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20trees%20were%20cut%20after%20the%20Lt%20Governor's%20visit%20and%20asked%20the%20DDA%20counsel%20if%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdefending%20actions%20by%20the%20LG%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20documents%20placed%20on%20record%20which%20says%20LG%20directed%20to%20cut%20trees%2C%20how%20can%20you%20run%20away%20from%20this%3F%20are%20you%20defending%20the%20LG%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahesh%20Jethmalani%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20DDA%20vice-chairman%20Subhasish%20Panda%2C%20asked%20if%20the%20Lt%20Governor%20was%20informed%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20protecting%20the%20trees.%20To%20this%2C%20Justice%20Oka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20lighter%20vein%2C%20I%20have%20read%20that%20famous%20Sherlock%20Holmes%20story%20-%20the%20secret%20why%20the%20dog%20did%20not%20bark.%26quot%3B%20The%20judge%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20short%20story%2C%20The%20Adventure%20of%20Silver%20Blaze%2C%20in%20which%20a%20horse%20is%20stolen%20but%20a%20dog%20that%20sees%20it%20does%20not%20react%20because%20it%20is%20an%20inside%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20the%20truth%20and%20we%20expect%20better%20assistance%20from%20the%20DDA.%20We%20are%20pained%20to%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20valuable%20trees%20have%20been%20felled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20DDA%20vice-chairman%20if%20there%20is%20an%20official%20record%20of%20what%20transpired%20during%20the%20Lt%20Governor's%20visit.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20clear%20statement%20of%20facts%20from%20the%20VC%2C%20because%20if%20what%20is%20indicated%20in%20the%20emails%20is%20correct%2C%20then%20the%20felling%20of%20the%20trees%20was%20on%20the%20directions%20by%20the%20LG.%20We%20expect%20the%20DDA%20to%20come%20clean%20on%20this%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20affidavit%20of%20the%20DDA%20vice-chairman%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20entire%20blame%20has%20been%20shifted%20on%20the%20officers%20stating%20that%20they%20were%20responsible%20for%20directing%20the%20contractors%20to%20cut%20the%20trees%20without%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20issuing%20contempt%20notices%20to%20these%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20ordered%20that%20in%20all%20current%20and%20future%20contracts%2C%20DDA%20must%20include%20a%20clause%20that%20felling%20of%20trees%20is%20not%20permissible%20without%20the%20court's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20propose%20to%20hold%20a%20detailed%20enquiry%20into%20the%20acts%20of%20the%20DDA%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20destruction%20of%20several%20valuable%20trees%20and%20consequentially%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20environment.%20Such%20brazen%20acts%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20cannot%20be%20lightly%20brushed%20aside%20by%20this%20Court.%20If%20authorities%20are%20not%20performing%20their%20statutory%20and%20constitutional%20duties%2C%20the%20court%20has%20to%20give%20a%20loud%20signal%20to%20all%20authorities%20that%20the%20environment%20cannot%20be%20damaged%20in%20such%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20flagged%20DDA%20roping%20in%20serving%20judicial%20officers%20as%20legal%20advisors%20and%20directed%20the%20high%20court%20to%20take%20action.%20%26quot%3BHow%20are%20serving%20judicial%20officers%20working%20with%20DDA%20as%20legal%20advisors%3F%20What%20happens%20to%20the%20independence%20of%20judiciary%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0The%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719236580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F