e%20the%20option%20to%20take%20a%20re-test.%20%26quot%3BThe%20exam%20will%20be%20conducted%20on%20June%2023%2C%20and%20the%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20before%20June%2030%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20who%20did%20not%20appear%20for%20the%20re-test%20will%20have%20to%20accept%20their%20original%20scores%2C%20minus%20the%20grace%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20were%20the%20students%20awarded%20the%20grace%20marks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20awarded%20grace%20marks%20to%201%2C563%20students%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Closs%20of%20exam%20time.%E2%80%9D%20In%20awarding%20the%20grace%20marks%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20it%20followed%20the%20same%20formula%20that%20the%20court%20had%20approved%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-odd-grace-marks-method-raised-red-flags-in-neet-ug-5954387%5C%22%3ECLAT%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20a%20similar%20situation%20arose%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20after%20an%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20candidates%20scored%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%5C%22%3Eperfect%20720%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20the%20All%20India%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20(AIPMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20perfect%20scores%20were%20attributed%20to%20the%20grace%20marks%2C%20which%20were%20first%20given%20because%20of%20a%20faulty%20question%20and%20logistical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Police%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20a%20few%20candidates%20had%20received%20the%20questions%20a%20night%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20NTA's%20attempts%2C%20a%20widespread%20accusation%20of%20leak%20resulted%20in%20nationwide%20protests%20and%20legal%20cases.%20Soon%20enough%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20intervened%2C%20reprimanding%20the%20NTA's%20handling%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20taken%20charge%20of%20the%20probe%2C%20following%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Human%20Resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retest%20took%20place%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20CBI%20registered%20an%20FIR%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20held%20on%20May%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F750-of-1-563-students-skipped-neet-ug-retest-exam-body-nta-5952815%5C%22%3ECBI%20filed%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20amid%20protests%20by%20students%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20paper%20leak%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719232560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happens-to-48-of-students-who-didn-t-turn-up-for-neet-ug-re-test-5959519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2048%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20students%20who%20were%20to%20retake%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%202024%20didn't%20turn%20up%2C%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happens-to-48-of-students-who-didn-t-turn-up-for-neet-ug-re-test-5959519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happens-to-48-of-students-who-didn-t-turn-up-for-neet-ug-re-test-5959519%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happens-to-48-of-students-who-didn-t-turn-up-for-neet-ug-re-test-5959519%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAct%20Now%2C%20Or...%26quot%3B%3A%20Experts%20Warn%20As%20Mumbai%20Struggles%20To%20Sleep%20Amid%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20is%20living%20up%20to%20its%20tagline%20'the%20city%20never%20sleeps'%20with%20temperatures%20soaring%20to%20record%20highs%20and%20affecting%20the%20sleep%20patterns%20of%20residents%2C%20say%20experts.%20Global%20warming%20has%20ushered%20in%20unprecedented%20warmth%20during%20the%20night%2C%20disrupting%20the%20sleep%20patterns%20of%20its%20residents%20and%20impacting%20their%20health%20adversely%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20study%20by%20Climate%20Central%20and%20Climate%20Trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20highlights%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20warm%20nights%20across%20Mumbai%2C%20with%20temperatures%20soaring%20above%2025%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20with%20an%20additional%2065%20unusually%20hot%20nights%20this%20year%20alone.%20This%20trend%20isn't%20restricted%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20other%20Maharashtra%20cities%20like%20Thane%2C%20Bhiwandi%2C%20and%20Ulhasnagar%20have%20also%20reported%20a%20surge%20in%20warm%20nights.%20Thane%20and%20Bhiwandi%20recorded%2070%20additional%20hot%20nights%20this%20summer%2C%20but%20Kalyan-Ulhasnagar%20topped%20the%20list%20with%2072.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20Trends'%20Kartiki%20Negi%20underscores%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20noting%20that%20several%20cities%20have%20shattered%20records%20spanning%20five%20decades%20due%20to%20climate%20impacts.%20This%20alarming%20rise%20in%20nighttime%20temperatures%20isn't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20discomfort%3B%20it's%20a%20health%20hazard%20affecting%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20act%20now%2C%20nights%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20hot%2C%20long%2C%20and%20sleepless%2C%20especially%20for%20vulnerable%20populations%2C%26quot%3B%20cautioned%20Kartiki%20Negi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20the%20sentiment%2C%20Pranav%20Garimella%20of%20the%20World%20Resources%20Institute%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BStudies%20have%20repeatedly%20shown%20that%20prolonged%20exposure%20to%20high%20night-time%20temperatures%20can%20lead%20to%20sleep%20deprivation%2C%20exacerbating%20existing%20health%20issues%20and%20impacting%20productivity.%26quot%3B.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20industries%20like%20agriculture%20and%20construction%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%2C%20facing%20potential%20productivity%20losses%20and%20health%20risks%20for%20their%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rising%20daytime%20temperatures%20and%20increasingly%20warm%20nights%2C%20preparations%20at%20both%20individual%20and%20institutional%20levels%20would%20be%20needed%20to%20mitigate%20the%20dual%20impact%20on%20health%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719231180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9067kji_mumbai-getty_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fsleepless-summer-in-mumbai-as-temperatures-soar-experts-warn-of-health-risks-5959272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20is%20living%20up%20to%20its%20tagline%20'the%20city%20never%20sleeps'%20with%20temperatures%20soaring%20to%20record%20highs%20and%20affecting%20the%20sleep%20patterns%20of%20residents%2C%20say%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fsleepless-summer-in-mumbai-as-temperatures-soar-experts-warn-of-health-risks-5959272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fsleepless-summer-in-mumbai-as-temperatures-soar-experts-warn-of-health-risks-5959272%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fsleepless-summer-in-mumbai-as-temperatures-soar-experts-warn-of-health-risks-5959272%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnilateral%20Discussions...%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20To%20PM%20On%20Bangladesh%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20objecting%20to%20the%20talks%20on%20water%20sharing%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20Bangladesh%20--%20a%20session%20Bengal%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20attend.%20Turning%20down%20the%20Centre's%20proposal%20for%20sharing%20of%20Teesta%20water%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20unilateral%20deliberations%20and%20discussions%20without%20consultation%20and%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20state%20government%20is%20neither%20acceptable%20nor%20desirable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20on%20sharing%20of%20Ganga%20and%20Teesta%20waters%20took%20place%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20when%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20visited%20Delhi%20--%20days%20after%20she%20came%20to%20attend%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20his%20historic%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20renewing%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20Farakka%20Treaty%20(1996)%20which%20is%20to%20expire%20in%202026.%20It%20is%20a%20treaty%20which%20delineates%20of%20sharing%20of%20water%20between.%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20and%20as%20you%20are%20aware%20it%2C%20has%20huge%20implications%20for%20the%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20wrote.%20The%20people%20of%20Bengal%2C%20she%20added%2C%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20sufferers%26quot%3B%20of%20such%20treaties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal%20has%20cooperated%20with%20Bangladesh%20on%20several%20issues%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20added%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20exchange%20of%20India-Bangladesh%20enclaves%2C%20Indo-Bangladesh%20Railway%20Line%20and%20bus%20services.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20water%20is%20very%20precious%20and%20is%20the%20lifeline%20of%20the%20people.%20We%20cannot%20compromise%20on%20such%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20which%20has%20severe%20and%20adverse%20implication%20on%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20proposed%20sharing%20the%20waters%20of%20Teesta%2C%20a%20river%20in%20north%20Bengal%2C%20she%20said%20the%20health%20of%20Teesta%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20has%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%26quot%3B%20much%20already%20due%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20several%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20deforestation%20in%20the%20river's%20upper%20catchment%20area%2C%20and%20now%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20water%20to%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20proposed%20a%20bilateral%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20for%20restoration%20of%20Teesta%20in%20Bangladesh.%20I%20am%20surprised%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20concrete%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20ministry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20to%20restore%20the%20river%20in%20its%20original%20form%20and%20health%20on%20the%20India%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20reasons%20stated%20above%2C%20water%20flow%20in%20Teesta%20has%20gone%20down%20over%20the%20years%20and%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20if%20any%20water%20is%20shared%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%20lakhs%20of%20people%20in%20north%20Bengal%20will%20get%20severely%20impacted%E2%80%A6%20therefore%20it%20is%20not%20feasible%20to%20share%20Teesta%20water%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719230700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc22udbo8_mamata-banerjee-pm-modi_625x300_01_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funilateral-discussions-mamata-banerjee-to-pm-on-bangladesh-talks-5959096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20objecting%20to%20the%20talks%20on%20water%20sharing%20between%20Centre%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20session%20Bengal%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20attend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funilateral-discussions-mamata-banerjee-to-pm-on-bangladesh-talks-5959096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funilateral-discussions-mamata-banerjee-to-pm-on-bangladesh-talks-5959096%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funilateral-discussions-mamata-banerjee-to-pm-on-bangladesh-talks-5959096%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sex%20Crimes%20Accused%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20To%20Remain%20In%20Jail%20Till%20July%208%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20facing%20charges%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20back%20to%20judicial%20custody%20until%20July%208.%20He%20was%20remanded%20to%20a%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20starting%20June%2018%20until%20July%202.%20But%2C%20the%C2%A0Special%20Investigation%20Team%20or%20SIT%20-%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20cases%20against%20him%20-%20sought%20a%20body%20warrant%20against%20him%20and%20took%20him%20under%20custody%20that%20ended%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20cases%20against%20the%2033-year-old.%20He%20also%20faces%20charges%20of%20rape.%20The%20cases%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20came%20to%20light%20after%20pen%20drives%20containing%20explicit%20videos%20allegedly%20involving%20Mr%20Revanna%20were%20reportedly%20circulated%20in%20Hassan%2C%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20there%20on%20April%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECases%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20police%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20him%20on%20April%2028%20but%20he%20left%20for%20Germany%20a%20day%20before%20on%20April%2027.%20This%20case%20originally%20involved%20alleged%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20a%2047-year-old%20former%20maid.%20According%20to%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%2C%20Prajwal%20was%20named%20accused%20number%202%20while%20his%20father%20HD%20Revanna%20accused%20number%201.%20HD%20Revanna%20has%20been%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20this%20case.%20But%20later%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20alleged%20statement%20of%20the%20same%20woman%2C%20rape%20charges%20were%20added%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20case%20was%20registered%20by%20the%20CID%20on%20May%201%2C%20in%20which%20a%2044-year-old%20woman%20accused%20Prajwal%20of%20repeatedly%20raping%20her%20at%20gunpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20case%20was%20registered%20by%20the%20SIT%20on%20May%203.%20The%20age%20of%20the%20victim%20is%20said%20to%20be%2060%20years.%20She%20has%20also%20accused%20Prajwal%20of%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'Blue%20Corner%20Notice'%20seeking%20information%20on%20his%20whereabouts%20had%20earlier%20been%20issued%20by%20Interpol%2C%20following%20a%20request%20by%20the%20(SIT)%20-%20-%20via%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2031%2C%20SIT%20officials%20arrested%20him%20soon%20after%20he%20landed%20at%20Bengaluru%20airport%20from%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna%20failed%20to%20retain%20the%20Hassan%20parliamentary%20constituency%20in%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20constituency%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20polls%20a%20day%20before%20he%20left%20for%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719227940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Flp2ig4f8_prajwal-revanna_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fsex-crimes-accused-prajwal-revanna-to-remain-in-jail-till-july-8-5959014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20facing%20charges%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20back%20to%20judicial%20custody%20until%20July%208.%20A%20special%20court%20last%20week%20remanded%20him%20in%20judicial%20custody%20till%20June%2024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fsex-crimes-accused-prajwal-revanna-to-remain-in-jail-till-july-8-5959014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fsex-crimes-accused-prajwal-revanna-to-remain-in-jail-till-july-8-5959014%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fsex-crimes-accused-prajwal-revanna-to-remain-in-jail-till-july-8-5959014%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224-Phase%20Probe%2C%201%2C000%20Phone%20Numbers%3A%20CBI's%20Plan%20To%20Crack%20Paper%20Leak%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInvestigating%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leaks%20of%20the%20NEET%20and%20NET%20exams%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20dispatched%20teams%20to%20Bihar%20and%20Gujarat's%20Godhra%20to%20gather%20evidence.%20According%20to%20CBI%20sources%2C%20the%20investigation%20will%20proceed%20through%20four%20phases%2C%20scrutinizing%20every%20aspect%20from%20the%20creation%20and%20printing%20of%20exam%20papers%20to%20their%20distribution%20across%20various%20examination%20centres%20nationwide.%20The%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20these%20exams%2C%20has%20stringent%20protocols%20in%20place%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality%2C%20making%20any%20breach%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20officials%20are%20also%20focusing%20on%20individuals%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20preparation%2C%20printing%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20secure%20storage%20of%20exam%20papers%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20exams.%20These%20roles%20entail%20safeguarding%20the%20papers%20until%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20tests%20begin%2C%20highlighting%20potential%20points%20of%20vulnerability%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtilising%20a%20database%20of%201%2C000%20names%20and%20phone%20numbers%20compiled%20during%20previous%20investigations%2C%20CBI%20is%20tracing%20those%20who%20may%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20leaks.%20This%20data%2C%20obtained%20from%20multiple%20cases%20including%20Vyapam%2C%20aids%20in%20identifying%20suspects%20and%20establishing%20communication%20patterns%20that%20could%20reveal%20the%20nexus%20behind%20the%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20an%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20students%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam.%20Initially%20attributed%20to%20grace%20marks%20due%20to%20a%20faulty%20question%20and%20logistical%20issues%2C%20subsequent%20investigations%20by%20Bihar%20Police%20uncovered%20a%20different%20aspect%3A%20the%20exam%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20to%20select%20candidates%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20cancelled%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20claiming%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bintegrity%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20been%20compromised%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20transparency%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20UGC-NET%20June%202024%20Examination%20be%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses.%20Over%209%20lakh%20students%20took%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20which%20assess%20the%20eligibility%20for%20'Assistant%20Professor'%20for%20'Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20Assistant%20Professor'%20roles%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudent%20protests%20have%20been%20raging%20across%20the%20country%20since%20amplified%20by%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20huge%20political%20row.%20Cases%20were%20also%20filed%20in%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20or%20NTA%2C%20which%20conducted%20the%20exams%2C%20has%20been%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719227280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm6tes5mg_neet-protest_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-net-nta-probe-4-phase-probe-1-000-phone-numbers-cbi-plan-to-crack-paper-leak-cases-5958970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investigating%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leaks%20of%20the%20NEET%20and%20NET%20exams%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20dispatched%20teams%20to%20Bihar%20and%20Gujarat's%20Godhra%20to%20gather%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-net-nta-probe-4-phase-probe-1-000-phone-numbers-cbi-plan-to-crack-paper-leak-cases-5958970%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-net-nta-probe-4-phase-probe-1-000-phone-numbers-cbi-plan-to-crack-paper-leak-cases-5958970%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-net-nta-probe-4-phase-probe-1-000-phone-numbers-cbi-plan-to-crack-paper-leak-cases-5958970%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20JP%20Nadda%20Named%20Leader%20Of%20House%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Health%20Minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20JP%20Nadda%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today.%20Mr%20Nadda%20also%20holds%20th