terests%20in%20a%20befitting%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20party's%20leader%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Sasmit%20Patra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJD%20MPs%20this%20time%20will%20not%20be%20confined%20to%20speaking%20on%20issues%20only%2C%20but%20are%20determined%20to%20agitate%20if%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20ignores%20Odisha's%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20raising%20the%20demand%20for%20special%20status%20to%20Odisha%2C%20the%20BJD%20MPs%20will%20raise%20the%20issues%20of%20poor%20mobile%20connectivity%20and%20low%20density%20of%20bank%20branches%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOdisha's%20demand%20for%20revision%20of%20coal%20royalty%20has%20been%20ignored%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20This%20is%20causing%20great%20loss%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20who%20are%20deprived%20of%20their%20rightful%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20that%20the%20nine%20MPs%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20will%20act%20as%20a%20strong%20opposition%2C%20Mr%20Patra%20said%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20has%20given%20clear%20instructions%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20state's%20people%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20BJD%20would%20maintain%20its%20earlier%20stance%20of%20giving%20issue-based%20support%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20support%20to%20BJP%2C%20only%20opposition.%20We%20may%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20Odisha.%26quot%3B%20Later%2C%20Mr%20Patra%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20supporting%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJD%20president%20asked%20us%20to%20act%20as%20a%20strong%20and%20vibrant%20opposition%20if%20the%20NDA%20government%20continues%20to%20ignore%20the%20genuine%20demands%20of%20Odisha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20ni