0for%20some%20drastic%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20some%20VVIPs%20come%2C%20the%20streets%20and%20footpaths%20are%20immediately%20cleared...and%20it%20stays%20so%20till%20they%20are%20here.%20How%20is%20it%20done%20then%3F%20Why%20can't%20it%20be%20done%20for%20everyone%20else%3F%20Citizens%20are%20ratepayers...they%20need%20to%20have%20a%20clear%20footpath%20and%20safe%20place%20to%20walk%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFootpath%20and%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20walk%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20We%20tell%20our%20children%20to%20walk%20on%20footpaths%20but%20if%20there%20is%20no%20footpath%20left%20to%20walk%20on%2C%20what%20do%20we%20tell%20our%20children%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%20together%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20been%20saying%20they%20are%20working%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20has%20to%20do%20something%20drastically.%20It%20cannot%20be%20that%20the%20authorities%20are%20perpetually%20just%20wondering%20what%20to%20do%20and%20working%20on%20it.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20lack%20of%20will%2C%20because%20where%20there%20is%20a%20will%20there%20is%20always%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20counsel%20SU%20Kamdar%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%2C%20said%20periodic%20action%20is%20taken%20against%20such%20vendors%20and%20hawkers%20but%20they%20keep%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20BMC%20was%20also%20considering%20the%20option%20of%20underground%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20remarked%20in%20jest%20that%20the%20corporation%20was%20literally%20trying%20to%20bury%20the%20problem%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20the%20fine%20imposed%20by%20civic%20bodies%20on%20these%20vendors%2Fhawkers%20was%20irrelevant%20as%20they%20have%20higher%20sales%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20fine%20is%20pittance%20to%20them.%20They%20will%20pay%20and%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20suggested%20the%20BMC%20develop%20a%20database%20identifying%20all%20such%20hawkers%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20breach%20orders%20and%20come%20back%20with%20their%20stalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20there%20be%20a%20combing%20operation.%20Start%20with%20one%20street...the%20biggest%20trouble%20is%20identification.%20They%20keep%20coming%20back%20because%20they%20are%20not%20identifiable%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719222360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F18l5e7d_indian-economy-street-vendors-unsplash_625x300_25_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstreets-footpath-cleared-for-vvips-why-not-for-everyone-high-court-5957597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20said%20when%20streets%20and%20footpaths%20are%20cleared%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20other%20VVIPs%20for%20one%20day%2C%20why%20can't%20it%20be%20done%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20for%20everyone%20else%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstreets-footpath-cleared-for-vvips-why-not-for-everyone-high-court-5957597%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstreets-footpath-cleared-for-vvips-why-not-for-everyone-high-court-5957597%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstreets-footpath-c