ed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20in%20solar%20generation%20in%202023%20pushed%20the%20country%20past%20Japan%20to%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20solar%20power%20generator.%20It%20has%20climbed%20from%20ranking%20ninth%20in%202015.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20in%20clear%20sight%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20to%20achieve%20500%20GW%20of%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030.%20But%20as%20the%20energy%20transition%20is%20underway%20and%20industries%20hustle%20to%20do%20their%20bit%20to%20go%20solar%2C%20there%20are%20success%20stories%20emerging%20from%20pockets%20across%20India%20where%20households%2C%20farming%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20street%20vendors%20are%20championing%20a%20similar%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20stories%20of%20some%20women%20who%20are%20using%20solar%20power%20to%20scale%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Solar%20power%20for%20drying%20fruits%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Latika%20is%20a%20retired%20teacher%20who%20dived%20into%20the%20arena%20of%20solar%20power%20for%20farming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C