0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F320595%2Faward-winning-teacher-lata-satagopan-uses-puppetry-to-educate-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclear%20to%20her%20that%20teaching%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewasn%E2%80%99t%20her%20true%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20that%20continuing%20in%20that%20job%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20right%20path%20for%20me.%20Like%20in%20any%20other%20household%2C%20my%20parents%20suggested%20that%20I%20get%20married%20since%20I%20had%20completed%20my%20education.%20I%20considered%20their%20traditional%20option%20and%20agreed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20marriage%2C%20she%20spent%20some%20more%20years%20looking%20for%20a%20direction.%20In%202013%2C%20she%20started%20volunteering%20with%20the%20Art%20Of%20Living%20Foundation%20and%20it%20changed%20her%20life%20for%20good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20passion%20in%20social%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20both%20spiritual%20and%20social%20impact%20programmes%2C%20and%20I%20was%20particularly%20interested%20in%20the%20latter.%20I%20proposed%20and%20organised%20several%20programmes%20for%20them%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20my%20first%20volunteering%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeenu%20suggested%20a%20programme%20which%20became%20the%20foundation%20of%20most%20of%20her%20work%20to%20come.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20plan%20was%20to%20visit%2010%20schools%2C%20plant%20five%20trees%20at%20each%2C%20and%20educate%20the%20students%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20tree%20planting%20and%20environmental%20conservation.%20I%20intended%20to%20take%20up%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20of%20their%20time%2C%20focusing%20on%20environmental%20awareness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20agreed%20to%20her%20proposal%20since%20it%20required%20no%20additional%20resources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20child%20was%20very%20small%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%2010%20schools%20seemed%20manageable.%20The%20response%20from%20these%20schools%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive%2C%20and%20soon%20more%20requests%20started%20pouring%20in.%20Within%20three%20months%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20cover%2030%20schools%2C%20which%20was%20my%20maximum%20capacity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20successful%20project%20became%20her%20motivation%20to%20undertake%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F137931%2Fsocial-impact-fund-infuse-ventures-gold-farm-money%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20social%20impact%20initiatives.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeenu%20also%20started%20to%20grow%20her%20circle%20and%20started%20volunteering%20and%20designing%20more%20programmes%20for%20different%20organisations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20I%20had%20to%20move%20to%20Kochi.%20When%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20any%20contacts%20in%20social%20work%20so%20I%20joined%20some%20volunteer%20groups.%20These%20groups%20were%20very%20active%20in%20helping%20with%20blood%20donations%20and%20other%20minor%20requests%2C%20gathering%20support%20for%20various%20causes.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Kerala%20experienced%20one%20of%20the%20most%20devastating%20floods%20in%20its%20history.%20I%20came%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20very%20prominent%20person%20via%20social%20media%20who%20was%20conducting%20relief%20efforts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collective%20efforts%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20helped%20provide%20relief%20to%20many%20in%20the%20affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221