0motivation%20that%20came%20from%20helping%20people%20in%20need%20kept%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Neenu%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20for%20her%20to%20work%20on%20her%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20heart%2C%20it%20was%20more%20like%20a%20project%20for%20me%20and%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur.%20After%20it%20was%20incubated%20at%20NSRCEL%20(Nadathur%20S.%20Raghavan%20Centre%20for%20Entrepreneurial%20Learning)%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20realised%20this%20initiative%20had%20much%20more%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20for%20Social%20Town%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-profit%20organisation%20was%20started%20with%20500%20people%20and%20has%20engaged%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20in%20social%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20initially%20used%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20emails%20for%20interactions.%20We%20used%20the%20platforms%20to%20dissipate%20important%20information%20about%20policy%20changes%2C%20incubation%20programmes%2C%20and%20more%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20organisation%20does%20not%20charge%20any%20fee%20for%20membership%20and%20is%20open%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20bring%20social%20change.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20more%20like%20a%20community%20of%20people%20with%20a%20similar%20school%20of%20thought%20who%20want%20to%20bring%20some%20kind%20of%20change%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20organisation%20works%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20changemaker%20in%20Kerala%20who%20wants%20to%20help%20a%20dying%20school%20and%20wants%20to%20give%20them%20computer%20systems%20but%20is%20unsure%20of%20whi