india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381-150x264.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-11-at-19.04.13-1-min-1718768381.jpeg%20908w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22881%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20decorations%20were%20all%20locally%20sourced%20and%20were%20later%20composted%20at%20the%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20her%20wedding%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20principles.%20She%20realised%20that%20all%20she%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20seek%20inspiration%20from%20weddings%20held%20three%20to%20four%20decades%20ago%2C%20like%20her%20parents%E2%80%99.%20Before%20the%20advent%20of%20small%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20large%20budgets%2C%20weddings%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerally%20sustainable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20weren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20have%20a%20simple%20wedding%20with%20a%20few%20guests%2C%20the%20chosen%20venue%20was%20the%20family%20farm.%20The%20next%20step%20was%20decorations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20go%20local.%20We%20chose%20locally%20available%20mango%20and%20coconut%20leaves%20for%20decorations%2C%20which%20could%20be%20composted%20too.%20While%20reusable%20steel%20%3Cem%3Emantapas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20available%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20go%20with%20a%20sugarcane%20one%20as%20it%20is%20traditionally%20used%20and%20grows%20in%20Shivamogga.%20It%20is%20also%20something%20that%20our%20cows%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Poorvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20shared%20her%20vision%20with%20the%20decorators%2C%20they%20came%