e%20memory%20continues%20to%20be%20etched%20in%20the%2037-year-old%E2%80%99s%20mind%2C%20as%20she%20settles%20down%20for%20a%20t%C3%AAte-%C3%A0-t%C3%AAte%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudhir%20Dave%20did%20not%20ever%20want%20his%20daughter%20to%20give%20up%20on%20her%20passion%20for%20want%20of%20a%20good%20coach.%20And%20so%20when%20in%202008%2C%20Hetal%20showed%20signs%20of%20wanting%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20sumo%20wrestling%2C%20Sudhir%20made%20one%20thing%20clear.%20If%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20coach%20available%2C%20he%20would%20become%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20four-year-long%20career%20in%20the%20Japanese-origin%20sport%2C%20Hetal%20has%20enjoyed%20the%20resounding%20cheers%20of%20the%20audience%2C%20the%20thrill%20of%20adrenaline%20while%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Edohyo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20ring%20where%20sumo%20wrestling%20happens)%2C%20and%20the%20adulation%20of%20the%20country.%20But%20outshining%20all%20of%20these%20is%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lengths%20to%20which%20her%20father%20went%20to%20show%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20working%20when%20I%20first%20got%20interested%20in%20sumo%20wrestling.%20The%20day%20he%20decided%20to%20be%20my%20coach%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338546%2Fmillet-startup-revenue-in-crores-ready-to-eat-food-health-sutra-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20his%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20devote%20all%20his%20time%20to%20training%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hetal%20recounts.%20How%20tough%20was%20it%20to%20take%20this%20life-altering%20decision%20on%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%3F%20Sudhir%20responds%2C%20%E2%80%9CHumans%20have%20crazy%20minds%20and%20when%20the%20mind%20decides%20it%20wants%20something%2C%20nothing%20is%20an%20obstacle%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiecing%20the%20story%20together%20of%20how%20