%20the%20organisers%20that%20I%20did%20not%20have%20one%2C%20they%20gave%20me%20one%20and%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20tie%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20she%20also%20got%20to%20be%20privy%20to%20the%20rituals%20that%20precede%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fthe-indian-pehlwan-who-saved-lives-during-partition-inspired-bruce-lee-with-his-regime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sumo%20wrestling%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20sitting%20intently%20and%20watching%20them%20train%20and%20observing%20their%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20The%20weight%20of%20the%20occasion%20dawned%20on%20her%2C%20but%20she%20points%20out%20that%20all%20fright%20lay%20forgotten%20when%20she%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20ring%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20was%20met%20by%20thunderous%20applause.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20stadium%20was%20cheering%20for%20me%20because%20the%20announcer%20had%20mentioned%20that%20I%20had%20come%20all%20alone%20from%20India%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20is%20riveting%20and%20gives%20Hetal%20goosebumps.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20first%20global%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20among%20the%20top%2010%20%E2%80%94%20propelled%20her%20towards%20the%20ones%20that%20followed.%20At%20the%20World%20Games%20in%202009%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20female%20athlete%20from%20India%20out%20of%20200%20competing%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20win%2C%20Hetal%20had%20to%20retire%20in%202012%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20sponsorship.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20she%20underscores%20lack%20of%20support%20as%20the%20biggest%20hurdle%20that%20stops%20women%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuing%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20sumo%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20have%20kept%20her%20on%20her%20toes%20with%20the%20documentary%20film%20%E2%80%98Sumo%20Didi%E2%80%99%2C%20directed%20by%20Jayant%20Rohatgi.%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20film%20is%20essayed%20by%20Shriyam%20Bhagnani.%20And%20Hetal%2C%20who%20personally%20trained%20Bhagnani%2C%20says%20the%20intent%20was%20to%20bring%20forth%20every%20emotion%20that%20has%20coloured%20the%20canvas%20of%20her%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pressure%20to%20make%20your%20country%20proud%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20not%20knowing%20the%20opponent%E2%80%99s%20next%20move%20in%20the%20ring%2C%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20alone%20sometimes%20at%20tournaments%20and%20not%20having%20anyone%20to%20look%20at%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20the%20desire%20to%20prove%20people%20who%20said%20%E2%80%98You%E2%80%99re%20fat%2C%20you%20cannot%20do%20anything%20in%20life%E2%80%99%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20hopeful%20that%20her%20story%20will%20be%20a%20beacon%20for%20people%20to%20believe%20in%20themselves%20and%20follow%20their%20calling.%20And%20behind%20Hetal%20stands%20a%20proud%20father%20who%20never%20for%20once%20doubted%20that%20his%20daughter%20would%20achieve%20these%20feats%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMhari%20chori%20chore%20se%20kam%20hai%20ke%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20all%20those%20who%20questioned%20how%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20simple%20diet%20would%20let%20her%20achieve%20greatness%20in%20sports%2C%20her%20father%20has%20an%20answer%20ready%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEk%20marwari%20ne%20daal%20bhat%20kha%20ke%20history%20bana%20li%3C%2Fem%3E%20(A%20%3Cem%3EMarwari%3C%2Fem%3E%20girl%20has%20created%20history%20despite%20a%20simple%20vegetarian%20diet).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3