A%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20suggests%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20seen%2016%2C344%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20since%201%20March%20this%20year%2C%20with%20486%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20on%2022%20May%20alone.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Epointed%20out%20that%20in%20Ahmedabad%20alone%2C%20the%20city%20recorded%2045%20cases%20of%20heat%20strokes%20last%20summer%20with%20no%20comprehensive%20data%20on%20heat-related%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20home%20solutions%20like%20dampening%20the%20curtains%20of%20their%20entrances%20and%20throwing%20water%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20roof%20worked%2C%20they%20all%20were%20temporary%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20situation%20into%20careful%20consideration%2C%20an%20organisation%20called%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT)%20came%20up%20with%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20the%20slum%E2%80%99s%20heat%20woes.%20If%20you%20now%20look%20at%20the%20roofs%20of%20most%20of%20these%20homes%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F106622%2Fmahesh-desai-helpline-education-home-ahmedabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20slums%20of%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view%2C%20you%20will%20find%20them%20all%20painted%20in%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint%20so%20as%20to%20cool%20the%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMHT%20representatives%20came%20to%20us%20and%20told%20us%20about%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint.%20We%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20reasonable%20thing%20to%20do.%20After%20painting%20our%20roof%20white%2C%20we%20noticed%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20temperature%20inside%20our%20house.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20feels%20much%20more%20comfortable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Radha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20am%20at%20work%2C%20my%20mother%20stays%20at%20home%20all%20day%2C%20and%20she%20also%20feels%20much%20better%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20slum%20dwellers%20survive%20the%20heatwave%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavna%20Maheriya%2C%20MHT%E2%80%99s%20programme%20manager%2C%20shares%20about%20the%20living%20conditions%20of%20slum%20dwellers.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20main%20concern%20at%20this%20point%20is%20to%20survive.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%2050%20degrees%20outside%20and%20the%20Government%20issues%20warnings%20of%20a%20heatwave%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20earn%20their%20food%20for%20the%20night.%20Heat%20action%20is%20their%20last%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20has%20helped%20women%20in%20slums%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20in%20their%20homes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353028%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20has%20helped%20women%20in%20slums%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20in%20their%20homes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20heat%20is%20so%20much%2C%20the%20rooms%20heat%20up%20too%2C%20becoming%20hotter%20than%20outside%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20proper%20ventilation%2C%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20care%20of%20the%20heat%2C%20it%20becomes%20our%20duty%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%20The%20trust%20works%20in%20different%20areas%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20initiatives%20that%20we%20have%20taken%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20started%20as%20a%20pilot%20in%202016%20when%20the%20trust%20was%20looking%20into%20cheaper%20and%20innovative%20ways%20of%20reducing%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%20has%20been%20working%20in%20different%20areas%20such%20as%20pollution%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20etc%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20started%20working%20for%20efficient%20energy%20and%20helped%20a%20lot%20of%20rural%20people%20in%20Ahmedabad%20have%20legal%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%20they%20used%20to%20get%20electricity%20illegally%20from%20poles%20or%20from%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20connection%20by%20paying%20them%20a%20small%20amount.%20This%20was%20illegal%20and%20highly%20dangerous.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20people%20switched%20to%20legal%20connections%20with%20authorised%20metres%2C%20the%20bills%20started%20to%20flow%20in.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20complained%20about%20high%20electricity%20bills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20MHT%20team%20inspected%20the%20homes%20of%20these%20people%20and%20realised%20that%20they%20were%20using%20100-watt%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20small%20home%20with%20one%20or%20two%20rooms%2C%20high%20bills%20are%20not%20possible.%20We%20noticed%20that%20the%20homes%20did%20not%20have%20proper%20ventilation%20due%20to%20shared%20walls.%20They%20have%20the%20kitchen%20in%20the%20same%20rooms%2C%20which%20also%20contributed%20to%20increasing%20the%20heat%20inside%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reduce%20the%20heat%2C%20people%20used%20to%20run%20fans%20and%20coolers%20the%20entire%20day%20at%20full%20speed%2C%20increasing%20the%20bill.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20us%20realise%20that%20changing%20their%20bulbs%20would%20not%20solve%20the%20problem.%20We%20needed%20a%20heat%20action%20plan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20UV%20reflective%20paint%20not%20only%20brings%20down%20the%20temperature%20but%20also%20reduces%20electricity%20bills%20due%20to%20less%20usage.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20UV%20reflective%20paint%20not%20only%20brings%20down%20the%20temperature%20but%20also%20reduces%20electricity%20bills%20due%20to%20lesser%20usage.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20ray%20of%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavna%20takes%20us%20through%20the%20various%20pilots%20and%20schemes%20it%20launched%20before%20the%20UV%20white%20paint%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20introduced%20initiatives%20which%20modified%20their%20roofs.%20We%20introduced%20a%20fibre%20sheet%20roof%2C%20placed%20in%20a%20dome%20style%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejaali%20%3C%2Fem%3Estructure%20for%20ventilation.%20This%20not%20only%20improved%20the%20ventilation%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20heat.%20This%20plan%20became%20very%20popular%20and%20we%20installed%20it%20in%20nearly%20500%20homes.%20In%202013%2C%20we%20introduced%20another%20pilot%20called%20modular%20roofs.%20The%20reduction%20in%20temperature%20was%20five%20to%20six%20degrees%20but%20the%20product%20needed%20a%20lot%20of%20modifications%20in%20the%20existing%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20had%20pilots%20like%20thermocol%20false%20ceilings%20and%20bamboo%20ceilings%20too.%20It%20was%20in%202016%20that%20we%20introduced%20the%20rooftop%20white%20paint.%20The%20paint%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20by%20five%20to%20six%20degrees%20inside%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20the%20cool%20roof%20technology%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20thing%20about%20this%20initiative%20was%20that%20the%20application%20was%20very%20easy.%20The%20women%20could%20easily%20source%20it%20from%20us%20and%20apply%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20Ahmedabad%20Heat%20Action%20Plan%20committee%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20cool%20roof%20technology%20works.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20included%20our%20cool%20roof%20technology%20in%20their%20revised%20plan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20various%20initiatives%20are%20launched%2C%20many%20steps%20are%20taken%20to%20ensure%20they%20benefit%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20are%20structural%20changes%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20slum%20dwellers%2C%20we%20give%20them%20a%20100%20percent%20guarantee%20that%20if%20the%20technology%20does%20not%20suit%20them%2C%20we%20will%20reverse%20all%20the%20changes%20made%20to%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20over%2020%2C000%20slum%20homes%20in%20Ahmedabad%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20in%20slum%20areas%20are%20given%20proper%20induction%20before%20a%20project%20is%20implemented%20in%20their%20homes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20in%20slum%20areas%20are%20given%20proper%20induction%20before%20a%20project%20is%20implemented%20in%20their%20homes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20about%20this%20white%20paint%20and%20its%20benefits%20during%20a%20Community%20Action%20Group%20(CAG)%20meeting%20supported%20by%20the%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT).%20They%20gave%20us%20a%20poster%20that%20had%20details%20about%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint.%20We%20understood%20that%20it%20helps%20reduce%20the%20heat%20inside%20our%20houses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20house%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20ventilation.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20so%20hot%20during%20the%20summer%20that%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sit%20inside%20comfortably.%20But%20after%20we%20applied%20the%20paint%20on%20our%20roof%2C%20it%20feels%20much%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20Ignas%20Park%20slum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20trust%20depends%20on%20funds%20and%20contributions%20to%20continue%20helping%20the%20people%20living%20in%20slums%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3xicHzY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20how%20you%20can%20help%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20credit%3A%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718284321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20assisting%20women%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20is%20using%20cool%20roof%20technology%20to%20help%20them%20escape%20the%20heat%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20This%20initiative%20has%20made%20over%2020%2C000%20homes%20cooler%20and%20more%20comfortable%20during%20the%20heatwave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353012%2Fheatwave-mahila-housing-trust-reflective-solar-paint-ahmedabad-ignas-park-slum-homes%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coronavirus%3A%202nd%20Person%20Dies%20In%20U.S.%3B%20New%20Cases%20Reported%20In%20Florida%20And%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20second%20person%20has%20died%20from%20COVID-19%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20officials%20in%20Washington%20state%20say.%20With%20new%20coronavirus%20cases%20being%20reported%20in%20several%20states%2C%